<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.ReadWriteMutex.WriteLock.Unlock" Title="WriteLock.Unlock method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.ReadWriteMutex">ReadWriteMutex</PageRef> ->
    WriteLock.Unlock
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>WriteLock.Unlock</TypeRef> method releases the write lock manually. This allows a lock to be released early, however the lock will also be released when the lock object is destroyed.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void WriteLock::Unlock();]]></Code>
  </Section>
